__Resources:__

- [ctags](http://ctags.sourceforge.net/)


```terminal
sudo apt-get install ctags
ctags -R
ctags -R --exclude=*.js 
ctags -R --exclude=*.js . ~/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/gems/
```

```vim
:ptag say_hi
:pclose
:tags
:tag
:h CTRL-T
:h CTRL-]
:h usr_29.txt
```

```~/.vimrc
set ignorecase
```
